<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/water.css@2/out/water.css">
    <title>Setup</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Create a facebook page</h1>
    <div>
        <ol>
            <li>Go to <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/create" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Create facebook page</a> </li>
            <li>Create a page with whatever name you like</li>
            <li>Go to <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook Developer</a></li>
            <li>
                <ol>
                    <li>Press get started</li>
                    <li>Complete the registration process</li>
                    <li>add messenger as product</li>
                    <li>add your page</li>
                    <li>generate page access token and set the token
                        <form action="/token" method="post">
                            <input type="text" name="token">
                            <button type="submit">Set Token</button>
                        </form>
                    </li>
                    <li>fill in the callback url and verification token</li>
                    <li>
                        <div>url: <%= url+"/webhook" %></div>
                        <div>token: <%= verification %></div>
                    </li>
                    <li>Add subscriptions: messages and messages post_back</li>
                    <li>send a message to the page to grab your id</li>
                </ol>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>  
</body>
</html>